data.description: Come check out this homestead with a stocked pond, a pavilion, chicken coops, a goat pen, and multiple outbuildings. These include a large detached garage, and a storage shed. This home is move in ready with a new roof, garden beds, and even a functioning hot tub to go with it. This could be a nice opportunity for a family or a retired couple. While it's just an hour from St. Louis, the property sits right off highway 30 near the Lonedell School District.
